{"tid":508363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少婦偕夫談心墮海 勇警17°C下海救人","createTime":"2017-12-24T07:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T10:58:27.000Z","uid":32938,"like":39,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"092bc330422349e4eec18887a334a10ea85c2f33","tid":508363,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/HBrR18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FHBrR18.jpg&h=d1a3a711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柴灣發生墮海意外。現場為嘉業街對開公眾填土躉船轉運站，凌晨零時許，一對夫婦坐在海邊石壆閒談，其間36歲姓陳妻子意外失足墮海，其36歲姓傅丈夫見狀，將一條麻繩拋落海中，讓妻子抓緊待援，自己則報警。 <br />\n<br />\n柴灣分區巡邏小隊警員到場，簡姓男警見情勢危急，卸下裝備跳入海中救人，將陳救上水警輪送回上岸，陳清醒送院治理。簡事後表示，當差22年，今次是首趟落海救人，被問及救到人是否感到開心，簡則指「（感覺）ok」。"},{"pid":"8dac38c3ab008d28ab89539eaa994ef73d881e15","tid":508363,"uid":101699,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:40:25.000Z","msg":"36<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d859b397883f399e239c4ef67d04652a61d52f7","tid":508363,"uid":52215,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"MILF<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1d288e2b437451844f3be91fcffb96435b1d61","tid":508363,"uid":142707,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9187f11df511c9d2c1394c47cd7502b9cd976c","tid":508363,"uid":119330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T07:50:01.000Z","msg":"幾得喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed0e05a46c707a69f1f112257dd1fb980c0e7bc","tid":508363,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"reply